title: Woman Fairy
description: A magical female creature found in myths and fantasy stories. Generally depicted as having insect-inspired wings, it can also be assumed to be quite diminutive in size.
apple_vendor_description: The woman fairy emoji, as seen on Apple devices, is a whimsical figure with delicate, translucent wings that shimmer with a soft, ethereal glow. Her form is sculpted with Apple's characteristic smooth gradients and gentle curves, suggesting a magical, benevolent presence. This enchanting emoji, with its subtle sparkle and graceful posture, is perfect for conveying wonder, fantasy, or a touch of playful magic in your messages.
